## 1ï¸âƒ£ SEO (Search Engine Optimization)

### ğŸ“Œ Definition

SEO is the process of optimizing a website to **rank higher on search engines** like Google **organically (without paid ads)**.

### ğŸ”‘ Types of SEO

* **On-Page SEO**

  * Keywords
  * Meta title & description
  * Headings (H1, H2)
  * Internal linking
  * Content quality

* **Off-Page SEO**

  * Backlinks
  * Guest posting
  * Social sharing
  * Brand mentions

* **Technical SEO**

  * Website speed
  * Mobile friendliness
  * SSL (HTTPS)
  * XML sitemap

### ğŸ¯ Goal

Increase **organic traffic**, visibility, and credibility.

